<title>USA: Sunbeam directors buy shares with own funds.</title>
<headline>Sunbeam directors buy shares with own funds.</headline>
<text>
<p>FORT LAUDERDALE, Fla., Aug 21 (Reuter) Sunbeam Corp said Wednesday that all of its outside directors have purchased shares of the company's comon stock with their own funds.</p>
<p>Charles Thayer and Howard Kristol bought 5,000 shares each and Richard Ravitch purchased 2,000 shares, the company said in a release Wednesday.</p>
